M|references|These case studies illustrate how lean principles work in practice. Each follows a consistent structure: the situation before lean methods were applied, the specific lean approach used, the experiment
M|references|1. [Case Study 1: Dropbox - The Smoke Test MVP](#case-study-1-dropbox-the-smoke-test-mvp)
